fects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/118149/', '', 'Methotrimeprazine, Promazine, Pimavanserin, Amisulpride, Triflupromazine', 'Ketotifen, Azelastine, Fexofenadine, Thiethylperazine, Desloratadine, Methdilazine', 1767369485);
