ects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/118231/', '', 'Amisulpride, Pimavanserin, Thiothixene', 'Paliperidone', 1767369485);
